<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title><%= ogTitle %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="<%= metaDescription %>">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f172a">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="AIRPET">
  <meta property="og:title" content="<%= ogTitle %>">
  <meta property="og:description" content="<%= ogDescription %>">
  <meta property="og:url" content="<%= ogUrl %>">
  <meta property="og:image" content="<%= ogImage %>">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/images/icons/icon-192.svg">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,400..700&family=Syne:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design-system.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landing-proteger.css">
</head>
<body class="validacao-landing min-h-screen antialiased">

  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/10 bg-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur-lg">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl tracking-tight text-white">AIRPET</a>
      <span class="hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white/90 bg-white/10 border border-white/15 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
        Validação com donos de pets reais
      </span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="lp-hero-mesh relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-12 pb-20 lg:pt-20 lg:pb-28">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
          <div>
            <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-400 mb-5">
              Lista de espera AIRPET
            </p>
            <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-[3.5rem] font-extrabold leading-[1.05] text-white tracking-tight">
              Seu pet pode desaparecer em segundos.
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
              Quando isso acontece, cada minuto pesa. O AIRPET nasce para reencontrar quem você ama — mais rápido que grupos e panfletos.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <a href="/lista-espera"
                 class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-400 text-white font-bold text-base px-8 py-4 shadow-xl shadow-primary-500/30 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]">
                Entrar na lista do AIRPET
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-primary-500/20 rounded-[2rem] blur-2xl"></div>
            <figure class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-white/10 aspect-[4/3] lp-img-fallback">
              <img src="/images/landing/hero.jpg" alt="Dono com seu cachorro em um momento de carinho"
                   class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="800" height="600" fetchpriority="high"
                   onerror="this.style.display='none'">
            </figure>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="lp-stat border-b border-gray-100">
      <div class="lp-stat-item">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
        Leva cerca de 2 minutos
      </div>
      <div class="lp-stat-item">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        Sem cartão · zero spam
      </div>
      <div class="lp-stat-item">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
        Feito para donos de pets
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-14">
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
            Você já sentiu que o tempo está contra você?
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">Não é falta de amor — é falta de um caminho claro quando tudo desaba.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <article class="lp-card-lift bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-red-50 text-red-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">O coração dispara</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">A cabeça trava. Cada minuto sem notícia parece uma eternidade.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="lp-card-lift bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4M12 16h.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Você perde o controle</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Grupos, redes, panfletos… e nada garante que quem achou vai te encontrar.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="lp-card-lift bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-orange-50 text-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 001.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 001.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 00-3.42 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Os métodos falham</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Você faz de tudo, mas a sensação é sempre a mesma: está correndo contra o relógio.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-600 text-center">O que o AIRPET entrega</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center text-gray-900 mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto tracking-tight">
          Proteção no momento em que mais importa
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-14 lp-bento gap-5">
          <article class="lp-card-lift lp-bento-main rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-white overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img src="/images/landing/solution-identify.jpg" alt="Cachorro olhando para a câmera" class="w-full h-52 sm:h-64 object-cover" loading="lazy" onerror="this.classList.add('lp-img-fallback'); this.style.minHeight='12rem'">
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Quem achou, sabe na hora de quem é</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">Sem adivinhação. A pessoa entende quem é o pet e que existe uma família esperando.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="lp-card-lift rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-white overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <img src="/images/landing/solution-contact.jpg" alt="Pessoa com celular perto do pet" class="w-full h-40 object-cover" loading="lazy">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">Contato direto com você</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Quem encontrou fala com você, o dono, na hora — sem depender da sorte em um grupo aleatório.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="lp-card-lift rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-white overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <img src="/images/landing/solution-location.jpg" alt="Cachorro em passeio na rua" class="w-full h-40 object-cover" loading="lazy">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">Por onde ele passou por último</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Um norte para onde procurar primeiro, quando cada rua parece igual.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 sm:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gray-900 px-8 py-14 sm:px-14 sm:py-16 text-center shadow-2xl">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 lp-hero-mesh opacity-60"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">Ajude a moldar o AIRPET</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
              Responda um formulário rápido e honesto. Suas respostas definem o que construímos primeiro — sem compromisso.
            </p>
            <a href="/lista-espera"
               class="mt-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-400 text-white font-bold text-lg px-10 py-4 shadow-xl shadow-primary-500/30 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]">
              Entrar na lista do AIRPET — ~2 min
            </a>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-slate-400">
              <a href="/privacidade" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">Política de privacidade</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-20 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 p-8 sm:p-10 text-center">
        <p class="font-display font-bold text-gray-900 text-xl">Estamos validando com donos de pets reais</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500 max-w-md mx-auto">Nada de promessa vazia. Queremos ouvir quem já sentiu esse medo na pele.</p>
        <p class="mt-6">
          <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white font-bold text-sm px-6 py-3 shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25">
            Vagas limitadas nas primeiras cidades
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-gray-100 py-10 text-center text-sm text-gray-500 bg-white">
    <p class="font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">AIRPET</p>
    <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> · <a href="/privacidade" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Privacidade</a></p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
